\par }{\fs20\cf0 Each of the special materials described below has a definite game effect. Some c
reatures have damage reduction based on their creature type or core concept. Some are resistant to all but a special type of damage, such as that dealt by evil-aligned weapons or bludgeoning weapons. Others are vulnerable to weapons of a particular materi
